OL,3,CHottest temperatures of the year so
OL,4,Cfar, but April showers loom
OL,6,FEnjoy some of the hottest temperatures
OL,7,Fof the year so far - April showers
OL,8,Fwill soon be back with a bang!
OL,10,FHow warm could it get in the next
OL,11,Fcouple of days?
OL,13,FThe April average is 13C and pretty
OL,14,Fmuch the whole of the UK will see
OL,15,Ftemperatures soaring well above that
OL,16,Fboth today and tomorrow.
