OL,3,CHottest temperatures of the year so
OL,4,Cfar, but April showers loom
OL,6,FHaving languished under cloud for much
OL,7,Fof this week, it's now the turn of the
OL,8,Fsouth and east where temperatures are
OL,9,Flikely to peak at 24C on Friday and
OL,10,FSaturday - which would make it our
OL,11,Fwarmest day of the year so far.
OL,13,FWhy are we going to see such a change
OL,14,Fin weather?
OL,16,FHigh pressure has been the heroine for
OL,17,Fseveral weeks - stretching across the
OL,18,FUK and blocking the advance of cloud,
OL,19,Fwind and rain-bearing frontal systems.
