OL,3,CHottest temperatures of the year so
OL,4,Cfar, but April showers loom
OL,6,FThat dominating high is now pulling
OL,7,Faway, allowing some potent frontal
OL,8,Fsystems to move in from the South and
OL,9,FWest from Sunday and throughout next
OL,10,Fweek.
OL,12,FHow much rain is expected?
OL,14,FQuite a lot! All parts of the UK will
OL,15,Fsee some rain but from Tuesday onwards
OL,16,Fsome areas could see as much as 60-
OL,17,F70mm in a short space of time (that's
OL,18,Ftwo-three inches).
