OL,3,CHottest temperatures of the year so
OL,4,Cfar, but April showers loom
OL,6,FBearing in mind that the monthly
OL,7,Faverage rainfall for April is 71mm -
OL,8,Fthat would be a month's worth of rain
OL,9,Fin just 24 hours.
OL,11,FWith that rain falling on very dry,
OL,12,Fhard-packed ground, any sustained
OL,13,Fdeluge has the potential to cause some
OL,14,Ftricky driving conditions and
OL,15,Flocalised flooding.
OL,17,FAlthough this is far from ideal for
OL,18,Fthe Easter holidays, it's worth
OL,19,Fremembering that we are now very much
OL,20,Fin need of that rain.
