OL,6,FNot at all! There is still the
OL,7,Fpotential for some lovely warm
OL,8,Fsunshine in between the rain and heavy
OL,9,Fshowers next week.
OL,11,FTemperatures will be cooler than this
OL,12,Fweek but still comfortably above
OL,13,Faverage - and we're still expecting
OL,14,Fthe sun to make some decent
OL,15,Fappearances.
OL,17,FJust don't forget some wellies and a
OL,18,Fbrolly along with your sunglasses and
OL,19,Fsun cream when you're out and about!
OL,21,FWhat about bank holiday weekend?
