OL,6,FStill a level of uncertainty here but
OL,7,Fit's likely that we will still be in
OL,8,Fthis changeable and unsettled regime
OL,9,Ffor at least the bulk of the Easter
OL,10,Fbank holiday regime.
OL,12,FAs we head into Easter Monday, we hope
OL,13,Fto see something a little drier and
OL,14,Fless lively.
OL,16,FAll in all, it's turning out to be a
OL,17,Fmost peculiar month!
